public Person(List<String> values,
              String insertOrder,
              String dateFormat)
       throws ParseException
Allows to create a person by passing a list of values. To create insertOrder String you must consider:
Consider the following positions:
  • lastName 0
  • fistName 1
  • gender 2
  • dateOfBirth 3
  • favoriteColor 4
If elements are ordered you should use insertOrder="01234"

Parameters:
values - ArrayList containing each person values
insertOrder - Contains position of elements to be inserted
dateFormat - Format used to parse dateOfBirth
Throws:
ParseException
